## Suggested commit message (user runs)

```bash
git add -A
git commit -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
feat(knowledge-engine-baseline): pack #5 phase 0 complete

Adds the foundation for the Knowledge engine:
- afa-contracts::knowledge::* — 9 types
  (KnowledgeRecord, RecordId,
  KnowledgeRecordInput, FindInformationRequest,
  FindInformationResponse, Topic,
  KnowledgeCapabilities, KnowledgeErrorV1,
  KnowledgeErrorKind) + 2 audit events
  (KnowledgeQueried, KnowledgeRecordStored) +
  the KnowledgeV1 trait + the 5-to-6 error
  mapping + 3 common-field accessors.
- afa-knowledge — new crate with re-exports
  and an empty conformance suite stub.
- afa-plugin-knowledge-json — new crate with
  7 submodules (adapter, config, index,
  search, storage, atomic_write, topic_slug)
  as skeletons; JsonKnowledgeAdapter struct
  with unimplemented!() methods pending
  Phase 1+ implementations.
- afa-kernel::CapabilityRegistry — additive
  register_knowledge(key, adapter,
  storage_root) and knowledge(key) methods +
  KnowledgeAlreadyRegistered { key } error
  variant + new knowledge: HashMap<String,
  (Arc<dyn KnowledgeV1>, PathBuf)> field.
- Workspace deps: uuid 1.23.4, tempfile
  3.27.0, proptest 1.11.0 (pinned per TRD
  §3.6).

Test count: 260 passing across 42 test
binaries (up from 230 in 33 in the Pack #4
baseline). +30 tests / +9 binaries: 19 in
afa-contracts::knowledge::* unit tests, 5 in
afa-kernel capability_registry, 1 in
afa-knowledge/tests/knowledge_v1.rs, 4 in
afa-plugin-knowledge-json module compile
tests, plus 1 new binary in
afa-knowledge/tests/. All 4 validation gates
green (fmt, clippy, test, doc).

EXPLAINED doc patched to match TRD on-disk
layout (one directory per topic, one .md
per record).

Phase 1 (write path: store_information +
atomic write + boot + KnowledgeRecordStored
event) is next.

Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
EOF
)"
```

